item.title: No-ip
item.dc:creator: @gunztheduel gunztheduel
item.description:
@gunztheduel wrote:

the_storm_001:

how do i get no-ip to work?? i downloaded it and installed it and setup my account and ive creadted a host and when i open up mopar i type localhost and i can get in but no1 else can

Dude, just follow this -

-> Download source

-> Register at http://www.no-ip.com/

-> Make host

-> Portforward (Portforward your computer IP -_-)

-> Compile and run

-> Open DUC and leave it on

-> Type in ‘localhost’ for your server name in client

-_-
